---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About Peter Etelej" description="Software developer and technical writer">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<div class="bg-hero-gradient dark:bg-hero-gradient-dark text-white py-16">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
				Software developer, system administrator, and technical writer
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Content -->
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
		<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
			<div class="flex items-center space-x-6 mb-8 not-prose">
				<div class="flex-shrink-0">
					<img 
						src="/images/etelej_avatar_small.png" 
						alt="Peter Etelej"
						class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full"
					/>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Peter Etelej</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
						Software Developer & Technical Writer
					</p>
					<div class="flex space-x-4 mt-3">
						<a 
							href="https://github.com/peteretelej" 
							target="_blank"
							class="text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700 dark:text-brand-400 dark:hover:text-brand-300"
						>
							GitHub
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p>
				Welcome to my technical blog! I'm a software developer with a passion for creating clean, efficient code and sharing knowledge through documentation and tutorials.
			</p>

			<h3>What I Write About</h3>
			<p>
				This blog focuses on practical, hands-on technical content including:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>System Administration</strong> - Ubuntu server setup, VPS management, and DevOps practices</li>
				<li><strong>Web Development</strong> - PHP, cURL, APIs, and backend development</li>
				<li><strong>Version Control</strong> - Git workflows, best practices, and advanced techniques</li>
				<li><strong>Development Tools</strong> - Command line utilities, automation, and productivity tips</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>My Approach</h3>
			<p>
				I believe in learning by doing and sharing practical knowledge that can be immediately applied. Each post is designed to be:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Technically accurate and up-to-date</li>
				<li>Step-by-step and easy to follow</li>
				<li>Focused on real-world scenarios</li>
				<li>Concise yet comprehensive</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>Get In Touch</h3>
			<p>
				Have questions about any of the tutorials or want to suggest a topic? Feel free to reach out through GitHub or connect with me on other platforms.
			</p>

			<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg not-prose">
				<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Quick Stats</h4>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
					<div>
						<span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Focus Areas:</span>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Backend Development, DevOps, System Administration</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<span class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Favorite Stack:</span>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">PHP, Python, Ubuntu, Git, Docker</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Base>
